<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="utf-8" /><meta content="IE=edge,chrome=1" http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" /><title>Dynamiczna zmiana folderu z szablonami w Merbie</title><link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Droid+Sans:400,700|Bitter:400,700,400italic|Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,700italic,400,300,700" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /><link href="../assets/stylesheets/all-f5ec2720.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /><script src="../assets/javascripts/all-eca7008a.js" type="text/javascript"></script></head><body class="x2009 x2009_dynamiczna-zmiana-folderu-z-szablonami-w-merbie"><div class="navbar navbar-default"><div class="navbar-collapse collapse navbar-responsive-collapse"><div class="container"><ul class="nav navbar-nav"><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Blog</a></li><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/about.html">About</a></li><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/projects.html">Projects</a></li><li><a class="navbar-brand" href="/talks.html">Talks</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="container"><article class="post"><div class="page-header"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-10"><h1>Dynamiczna zmiana folderu z szablonami w Merbie</h1></div><div class="col-md-2 post-date"><time datetime="2009-01-27">Jan 27, 2009</time></div></div></div><div class="alert alert-info">This article is written in Polish and was originally
<a href="http://teamon.jogger.pl/2009/01/27/dynamiczna-zmiana-folderu-z-szablonami-w-merbie">published at Jogger</a>.</div><div class="lead"><p>Tym razem będzie bardzo krótko. Potrzebowałem sprawdzenia za każdym razem wartości <code>Setting[:theme]</code> i na jej podstawie ustawić katalog &ldquo;poszukiwań&rdquo; pliku z szablonem &hellip;</p>
<pre class="highlight ruby"><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">Application</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="no">Merb</span><span class="o">::</span><span class="no">Controller</span>
  <span class="n">before</span> <span class="k">do</span>
    <span class="n">template_roots</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="o">[</span>
      <span class="s2">"themes"</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="no">Setting</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="ss">:theme</span><span class="o">]</span> <span class="sr">/ "views", :_template_location
    ]
  end
end
</span></pre>
<p>&hellip; i działa ;]</p>

<p>Dzięki temu nie trzeba przekazywać do każdego <code>display/render</code> bezwzględnej ścieżki do pliku.</p>
